    protected void manipulatePdf(String dest) throws Exception {
        //Initialize PDF writer
        PdfWriter writer = new PdfWriter(dest);
        //Initialize PDF document
        PdfDocument pdf = new PdfDocument(writer);
        //Initialize document
        Document document = new Document(pdf);
         document.setFontSize(10);
        //Add paragraph to the document
        Paragraph p = new Paragraph();
       
        p.setFixedLeading(0);
        document.add(p.add("RENTAL AGREEMENT FORM"));
       
        p = new Paragraph();
        p.setFixedLeading(0);
        document.add(p.add("HST Reg. No.\t:"+jTextField1.getText()));
        
        p = new Paragraph();
        p.setFixedLeading(0);
        document.add(p.add(jTextField2.getText()));

        
          p = new Paragraph();
        p.setFixedLeading(0);
        document.add(p.add(jTextField3.getText()));

        
        p = new Paragraph();
        p.setFixedLeading(0);
        document.add(p.add(jTextField4.getText()));

        //Close document
        document.close();
